short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple way to copy Youtrack tickets

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Copy Tickets or Issues card from JetBrains YouTrack as a table,
so you can paste the the card on any table (e.g. Google Docs)

- Activate the extension (on/off button)
- Go to your YouTrack Agile Board.
- Select cards you want to copy.
- Click extension icon then Copy Tickets button or
- Click copy icon on the right bottom

We don't collect any of your data. It just saved into your local storage.

Please feel free to suggest new features and report bugs.
